nodes.text: Hiu Woong-Sin is a Southeast Asian actor who portrayed Colonel Haxen Delto in Rogue One: A Star Wars Story. As the character was only later identified as Haxen Delto in Star Wars: Rogue One: The Ultimate Visual Guide, the film's IMDb entry credits Woong-Sin as Adjutant to General Draven.
